    Jupyter -->|"TCP/5432<br/>Credentials"| PostgreSQL
    Jupyter -->|"TCP/1433<br/>Credentials"| MSSQL
    Jupyter -->|"TCP/9092<br/>Configurable"| Kafka

    %% Infrastructure flows
    InternalRegistry -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>ImageStream import"| Quay

